# System Architecture & AI Model Reference (v2.0)
## Adaptive Sinhala Dyslexia Screening & Guidance Platform — R26-SE-031

> **v2.0 Revision:** Reflects the Multi-Dimensional Behavioral Signal Vector (MBSV) architecture.
> The previous ε-Greedy bandit, EMA-DKT, and RSI scalar have been replaced. Component ownership
> conflicts (BKT, gamification, content delivery) are fully resolved. Refer to the conflict
> resolution table in §2 before making any cross-component changes.

---

## 1. Full System Flow (MBSV Architecture)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph Flutter["📱 Flutter App"]
        OB["Guardian Onboarding\n(profile + VARK questionnaire)"]
        CALIB["Baseline Calibration\n(4 tasks, 10–12 min)"]
        TASKS["Learning Task Screens\n(Letter ID, Syllable Train,\nWord Match, Reading Fluency\nStory Sequence, Draw-a-Man...)"]
        WARMUP["SM-2 Warm-Up\n(session start, 2 min)"]
        STAGE1["Stage 1 Overlay\n(syllable split + audio)"]
        STAGE2["Stage 2 Activity\n(Tapping / Tracing /\nPicture-Word / Song)"]
        GAMEMODE["Gamification Overlay\n(mini-game, 2–3 min)"]
        GDASH["Guardian Dashboard\n(Mastery Heatmap + Alerts)"]
    end

    subgraph C1["🔍 C1 — CBME (Port 8011)"]
        TEL["/api/v1/telemetry\nReceive raw event batch"]
        WELF["Welford's Algorithm\nPersonalized Z-score baseline"]
        KALF["Kalman Filter\nTouch kinematics → kalman_innovation"]
        LGBM["LightGBM × 6\nOne model per MBSV dimension\n(Platt-scaled)"]
        SHAP_EP["/api/v1/monitoring/shap\nSHAP explanation endpoint"]
        ISO["Isolation Forest\nSession outlier flag (100%)"]
        MBSV_OUT["MBSV Output\nvisual_strain_index\ncognitive_load_index\nphonological_strain_index\nengagement_index\nsession_fatigue_index\nerror_pattern_vector"]
        TEL --> WELF --> KALF --> LGBM --> MBSV_OUT
        LGBM --> SHAP_EP
        LGBM --> ISO
    end

    subgraph C2["🎨 C2 — AVLI (Port 8014)"]
        SOVCM["SOVCM\nSinhala char complexity table"]
        LINUCB["LinUCB Contextual Bandit\nTypography arm selection"]
        TYPO["/api/v1/ui/typography\nReturn typography config\n(font, spacing, diacritic_offset,\nglyph_padding)"]
        GSTATE["Gamification State Machine\nengagement_index < 0.3 for 30s\n→ trigger mini-game"]
        SOVCM --> LINUCB
        LINUCB --> TYPO
    end

    subgraph C3["📚 C3 — PLCE (Port 8012)"]
        BKT["BKT Engine\nHidden Markov Model\n9-node Sinhala skill graph"]
        IRT["IRT 2PL\nContent difficulty calibration"]
        EBB["Ebbinghaus Decay\nMastery de-rating over time"]
        REPO["Content Repository\n~135 items × 9 skills"]
        NEXTI["/api/v1/content/next\nZPD-targeted content selection"]
        MAST["/api/v1/mastery\nmastery_vector endpoint"]
        BKT --> EBB --> NEXTI
        IRT --> NEXTI
        REPO --> NEXTI
        BKT --> MAST
    end

    subgraph C4["🧠 C4 — IIGE (Port 8013)"]
        SPLIT["Sinhala Unicode\nSyllable Splitter"]
        ERRCLF["Phoneme Error Analyser\n(Unicode + error_pattern_vector)"]
        RFWORD["Random Forest\nWord Difficulty Classifier"]
        SM2["SM-2 Scheduler\nPer-child, per-skill"]
        ACT["Activity Selection Matrix\nerror_type × mastery_level"]
        RTI["/api/v1/intervention/rti_alert\nTier 3 guardian alert"]
        SPLIT --> ERRCLF --> RFWORD --> ACT
        SM2 --> ACT
        ACT --> RTI
    end

    OB --> CALIB --> TASKS
    TASKS -->|"POST /telemetry\n(touch_events, audio_buffer,\nsession_latency, hint_count)"| TEL
    TASKS -->|"POST /mastery/update\n(skill_id, is_correct, latency_ms)"| BKT

    MBSV_OUT -->|"visual_strain_index\nengagement_index"| C2
    MBSV_OUT -->|"cognitive_load_index\nsession_fatigue_index"| C3
    MBSV_OUT -->|"phonological_strain_index\nerror_pattern_vector"| C4

    TYPO -->|"typography_config"| TASKS
    GSTATE -->|"game_mode_trigger"| GAMEMODE

    MAST -->|"mastery_vector"| C4
    NEXTI -->|"next_content_item"| TASKS

    C4 -->|"stage=1 syllable_segments"| STAGE1
    C4 -->|"stage=2 activity_type"| STAGE2
    SM2 -->|"sm2_review_words"| WARMUP
    RTI -->|"tier3_alert"| GDASH
```

