## 4. Data Flow Summary (v2.0)

| Step | From → To | Payload Key Fields |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| 1 | Flutter → C1 | `touch_events`, `session_latency_ms`, `replay_count`, `audio_buffer` |
| 2 | Flutter → C3 | `skill_id`, `is_correct`, `response_latency_ms` |
| 3 | C1 → MBSV Store | `mbsv` (6 dimensions) |
| 4 | C1 MBSV → C2 | `visual_strain_index`, `engagement_index` |
| 5 | C1 MBSV → C3 | `cognitive_load_index`, `session_fatigue_index` |
| 6 | C1 MBSV → C4 | `phonological_strain_index`, `error_pattern_vector` |
| 7 | C3 → C4 | `mastery_vector` (`{skill_id: p_know}`) |
| 8 | C2 → Flutter | `typography_config`, `game_mode_trigger` |
| 9 | C3 → Flutter | `next_content_item` |
| 10 | C4 → Flutter | `stage`, `syllable_segments`, `activity_type` |
| 11 | C4 → Guardian Dashboard | `tier3_alert`, `sm2_review_words` |

