## 5. What Each Model Solves (Research-Grounded)

| Research Problem | Dyslexia Indicator | Model | Component |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Detect visual processing effort | Increased letter scanning fixations | `LightGBM → visual_strain_index` | C1 |
| Detect phonological decoding difficulty | Slow naming speed, phoneme errors | `LightGBM → phonological_strain_index` | C1 |
| Detect cognitive overload | Processing speed deficit | `LightGBM → cognitive_load_index` | C1 |
| Personalize sensitivity per child | High between-child variability | `Welford's baseline` | C1 |
| Motor-control uncertainty as proxy | Fine-motor deficit | `Kalman Filter → kalman_innovation` | C1 |
| Adapt typography to visual stress | Wilkins visual stress | `LinUCB bandit` | C2 |
| Abugida-specific spacing | Diacritic detachment in Sinhala | `SOVCM + diacritic_offset arm` | C2 |
| Re-engage disengaged learner | Low motivation / fatigue | `Gamification state machine` | C2 |
| Track phonological skill mastery | Skill-level learning progression | `BKT (HMM)` | C3 |
| Schedule spaced review | Long-term forgetting curve | `Ebbinghaus decay + SM-2` | C3, C4 |
| Split Sinhala words into syllables | Phonological segmentation difficulty | `Unicode syllable splitter` | C4 |
| Classify phonological error type | Specific deficit: vowel vs. consonant | `Random Forest + Unicode features` | C4 |

---

## 6. Session State Machine

```
App Launch
    │
    ▼
[Session 0] Guardian Onboarding
    ├─ Profile creation
    ├─ VARK questionnaire (guardian-answered) ──→ C3: set learner tag
    └─ Baseline calibration (4 tasks, 10–12 min) ──→ C1: Welford initialization
                                                   ──→ C3: BKT init (all skills p_know=0.3)
                                                   ──→ Screening report → Guardian Dashboard
    │
    ▼
[Sessions 1+] Learning Session (20–25 min)
    │
    ├─ START ──→ C4: SM-2 warm-up (if any words due today)
    │         ──→ C3: select first content item (ZPD, VARK modality)
    │         ──→ C2: apply current typography config
    │
    ├─ DURING TASK (every 5s):
    │    ├─ C1: compute MBSV snapshot
    │    ├─ C2: if visual_strain > 0.6 for 10s → LinUCB step → new typography
    │    │       if engagement < 0.3 for 30s → gamification overlay → notify C3
    │    └─ C4: if phonological_strain > 0.45 for 5s → Stage 1
    │               still ≥ 0.45 after 10s → Stage 2 activity
    │
    ├─ TASK COMPLETE:
    │    ├─ C3: BKT update; select next content item
    │    ├─ C4: SM-2 update for Stage 2 words
    │    └─ C2: log reward signal for LinUCB
    │
    └─ SESSION END:
         ├─ C1: MBSV trend flagging (for next session)
         ├─ C3: session summary (skills attempted, mastery delta)
         ├─ C4: RTI Tier 3 alerts if any
         └─ Guardian Dashboard: updated with all session data
```

